snippet.title: Types of Chemotherapy
snippet.description: * Types of Chemotherapy Examples are Carmustine and Lomustine. Anti-metabolites: are drugs that interfere with a cell's RNA and DNA. Anti-metabolites work when cells are dividing.

snippet.title: Cancer Word List for Patients
snippet.description: * Cancer Word List for Patients Examples of nitrosureas include carmustine and lomustine. Nocturia: Frequent urination at night. Node-negative: Cancer that has not spread to the lymph nodes.
